{"tid":519611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次有2個security leak，有一個Intel AMD ARM CPU齊齊有份","createTime":"2018-01-04T14:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T15:40:17.000Z","uid":22054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d415b7676cf4422422bc3ecc54bf17b220b68d5d","tid":519611,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:00:44.000Z","msg":"有個叫Meltdown，intel問題<br />\n<br />\n另一個叫Spectre，Intel，AMD同ARM都會中<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2018/jan/04/meltdown-spectre-worst-cpu-bugs-ever-found-affect-computers-intel-processors-security-flaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2018%2Fjan%2F04%2Fmeltdown-spectre-worst-cpu-bugs-ever-found-affect-computers-intel-processors-security-flaw&d=yHAcfvO569tlFF1nKuFUn8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=021e5ea0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2018/jan/04/meltdown-spectre-worst-cpu-bugs-ever-found-affect-computers-intel-processors-security-flaw</a><br />\n<br />\n其中Meltdown could allow hackers to bypass the hardware barrier between applications run by users and the computer&rsquo;s core memory. Meltdown, therefore, requires a change to the way the operating system handles memory to fix, which initial speed estimates predict could affect the speed of the machine in certain tasks by as much as 30%.<br />\n<br />\nSpectre potentially allows hackers to trick otherwise error-free applications into giving up secret information. Spectre is harder for hackers to take advantage of but is also harder to fix and would be a bigger problem in the long term, according to Gruss.<br />\n<br />\nmeltdown就最多cut 30%效能，Spectre可能冇得救<br />\n<br />\n呢次真係電腦大爆炸"},{"pid":"1d3a9c3e5b49568349ae037c7dcd4023c48f32cb","tid":519611,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  諗起班a粉喪笑i 家個陣<im